Privacy Policy for ニキータ・パリク Discord Bot

We, the developers of the ニキータ・パリク Discord Bot, understand the importance of privacy and the protection of personal information. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and share information when you use the Bot.

Information We Collect
The Bot may collect certain information from users to enable its functionality, such as message content and user IDs. We may also collect non-personally identifiable information about how the Bot is used, such as frequency of use and interactions with the Bot.

Data We Store
The Bot may store user data, including message content and user IDs, for the purpose of enabling the Bot's functionality. We may also store non-personally identifiable data about the usage of the Bot, such as frequency of use and interactions with the Bot.

Use of Information
We use the information collected by the Bot to provide and improve the Bot's functionality, as well as to develop new features and services. We may also use the information to communicate with users regarding the Bot's functionality and to respond to user inquiries.

Disclosure of Information
We do not disclose any personally identifiable information collected by the Bot to third parties. We may disclose non-personally identifiable information to third parties for the purpose of analytics and other research purposes.

Security
We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected by the Bot from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Changes to the Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes to the Privacy Policy will be effective immediately upon posting to our website.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us at https://discord.gg/Xyk2TjeAMJ.

By using the Bot, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this Privacy Policy.
